These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel, fantasy, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | western       | time-travel | documentary        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: german, french, malaysian, thai
1. the thai is somewhere between the malaysian and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the thai is between the malaysian and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Nationality   | french   | thai | malaysian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, roller, ship
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the bike##7
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Transport   | roller | bike  | ship   | boat |

