.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, pineapple, zucchini, artichoke
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person eating artichoke##7
3. the person eating zucchini is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | grapefruit | artichoke       | zucchini |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

