.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
House: townhouse, tower, wooden, art-deco
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the tower house##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the wooden house##1
4. the german is somewhere between the tower house and the townhouse house##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House         | wooden | townhouse   | art-deco | tower |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

