.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, whist, bridge
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing whist is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
6. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing billiard##7
7. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Game   | backgammon    | bridge | billiard   | whist |

