.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, mirinda, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, spanish
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage          | iced-tea    | juice   | hot-chocolate | mirinda  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

