.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, tomato, cucumber, cherry
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the person eating tomato is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the person eating cherry is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person eating cucumber is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating garlic##7
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | cherry | cucumber | tomato | garlic |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

