1. the person who growsazalea is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who growslily is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person who growstulip##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
