.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, grey, lavender, green
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the person who likes green is somewhere between the person who likes black and the owner of the snake##7
2. the person who likes grey is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the person who likes lavender##6
4. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person who likes black is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | black | green | grey | lavender |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

