2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person driving the roller##6
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person driving the quad-bike##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | bus | snowmobile | roller |
| Sport   | tennis  | sailing    | climbing    | skiing  |

