2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the wooden house and the fan of house##7
3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the craftsman house is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
