3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere between the person who likes light-blue and the fan of metal##7
5. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person who likes lavender##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Color           | lavender | emerald | mauve | light-blue  |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | reggae   | salsa    | techno |

