3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
6. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre    | action   | fantasy  | epic  | romance |
| Transport   | jet-ski | quad-bike | bike | train    |

