.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, soy-milk, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person drinking iced-tea##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Beverage         | iced-tea    | soy-milk | mirinda     | juice |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 